て…", "…積を前提に、降雨量の雨水流出量や調整池からのオーバーフロー時の排水量と流出先環境への影響について、防衛省として再評価すべきではありませんか。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/291", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/293", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/295", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/297", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/299", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/301", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/303", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/305", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/307", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/309", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/311", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/313", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/315", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/317", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/319", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/321", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/323", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/325", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/327", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/329", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/331", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/333", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121113950X01020230425/335", "sentence": []}, {"url": "